KitKat::

She head voices above her and tried to get up. She managed to stand 
up on her wobbly legs and looked at them. She was panting heavily and 
her optics were bright red. "I...am....Kit....KitKat....I...am..."  
She fell back to the ground, moaning in pain in black wolf form. 

Camoflage::
She walked up to the bot and licked it's nose. "I think it needs help 
Blackfang. And besides, it's one of us. How can it be? Maybe we 
should try to fix it huh? And look. It looks like you."
